OL,5, A top US health official has warned the
OL,6, country is facing an epidemic of       
OL,7, loneliness that is as dangerous to     
OL,8, health as smoking 15 cigarettes a day. 
OL,10,FSurgeon General Vivek Murthy told BBC  
OL,11,FNews he was among millions of Americans
OL,12,Fwho have experienced a "profound sense 
OL,13,Fof loneliness".                        
OL,15,FUS health authorities are calling for  
OL,16,Fsocial isolation to be treated as      
OL,17,Fseriously as obesity or drug abuse.    
OL,19,FNearly 50% of all Americans are thought
OL,20,Fto have been affected.                 
